{"tid":245804,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人玩 Creativerse?","createTime":"2017-05-16T13:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T13:50:19.000Z","uid":64378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0741ec314b3f84c4d5afb2499fc3f05ea02d109b","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"有無人玩 Creativerse?<br />\n<br />\n係一個好似Minecraft 既 Game 黎，畫面好少少，亦多左d 新野，想詳細睇直接search creativerse 3dm/巴哈都會有<br />\n<br />\n岩岩上個禮拜出，依家steam 有得免費玩，不過免費玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過免費版有d recepie 唔用得。<br />\n<br />\n我試玩左大半日覺得幾好玩 有潛力做下一隻minecraft 就買左pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多左對翼同隨身燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開左個public world,叫 This is Hong Kong.<br />\n有興趣就一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者約埋一齊用支那人world 搞串個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af60b2d9fbb500386b43e46f846ab11aec2c1b0f","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8db35726bd63569446c59ecc4aca4ac8912ddf1a","tid":245804,"uid":264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接玩minecraft?"},{"pid":"bc1976497a3e51099a84ff9bed0b5b00344887b4","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"因為minecraft 玩得太耐開始到頂，就算狂裝mode, 佢個engine 都到頂<br />\n<br />\n咁未轉下新口味， 呢隻岩岩出，之後慢慢會愈來愈多mode 同新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f335f2e6a8e1681f19ce602dcfd824f615c3026","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"dcad8ece29c52adf791efb4488cef245cfc06a22","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1d52acf0a340b8e6bcdb40d8ded97113bdc5361b","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8200418f09d6ee3190ccefe3551b4591e6e7e852","tid":245804,"uid":425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"有玩 其實隻game要做d咩 目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494df3afdbee9c9916a13b68b89d85240d6ec5cf","tid":245804,"uid":81300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"同Minecraft最大分別係咩？"},{"pid":"a97b0e79b6c57b23eb30ca350fc5b295eb8e7a05","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有玩 其實隻game要做d咩 目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n目標因人而異，而家同5個朋友一齊起緊個城，由設計到搵材料都一齊做，幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58854736e92e7ff3822594dd99690cb6fc7d353e","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同Minecraft最大分別係咩？</blockquote><br />\n我會覺得係素材，機關，server setting<br />\n佢有好多款石，木，唔同色既磚<br />\n畫質detail 過minecraft，server 都算穩定+順<br />\n其次係機關，呢隻game 整機關無 Minecraft 既紅石系統咁複雜咁高技術，反而可以諗下點樣利用更多唔同機關。<br />\ngame 入面亦都有內置既逃出遊戲，可以逃戰下自己<br />\nserver 入面亦都有 Claim 地功能，可以享受同唔同玩家一齊玩，又唔怕人地會破壞/盜取你既資產同領地<br />\n其實最大分別係唔駛錢+ 容易安裝，本身我係第一個裝game既，好容易就可以拉到身邊既fd 一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecd449de894f2ed9f926623f24b14dc7feec0d3","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"我同班fd 入左個 public ser 叫「Asia Public Server」<br />\n<br />\n入面既玩家大多都好nice , server 長期有大約10個人 online, 有興趣可以入黎一齊玩"},{"pid":"3d4bfe5c0b5debb4849d12a67546d5a1e570b070","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c9fe7103d56b12f290c046fd19b637edaacdcfa4","tid":245804,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:53:36.000Z","msg":"睇咗啲YouTube 片 幾有趣<br />\n考完試玩下"},{"pid":"f517c46ff55eb4f18019fdea381ca5753875d2ea","tid":245804,"uid":72761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T18:23:19.000Z","msg":"Down左 摸索緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716b742a76b9cc13f2436760bfe01ae66e9c806c","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Down左 摸索緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩唔明可以問丫，識答盡量答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb36cec6d74f035b803c68c118d14f2ca2ab525","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76195375977473247367857043bde1212178be17","tid":245804,"uid":84115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"隻game好快就冇野玩<br />\n玩左兩日 基本上已經做晒可以做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30e8c5bc3737d4e4f57487a8f3e15ff50854cac","tid":245804,"uid":12032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講就係iOS 同android嘅分別"},{"pid":"2531b3b989b09c4f6ed900885398addb7c65baf3","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933fb4002f9272a77f579e75ea1fd5597f2e389c","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有玩 其實隻game要做d咩 目標係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個哲學問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左一開始出裝，然後解鎖晒d 野<br />\n之後就係個世界鳩Fing 既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你可以起豪宅<br />\n可以探險探到入地心<br />\n可以放火燒晒成個山再大叫燒山多謝燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以當pokemon go 咁捉動物<br />\n可以起怪物房然後入去大叫我要打十個<br />\n,etc. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我依家岩岩齊裝，解鎖解左一大堆<br />\n打算係河邊起翻間大宅<br />\n之後去湖心島，個度有座高山，係個山頂起翻個決鬥場for pvp"},{"pid":"3b0918588ca8a9f0f1a04681e71881747bf01794","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同班fd 入左個 public ser 叫「Asia Public Server」<br />\n<br />\n入面既玩家大多都好nice , server 長期有大約10個人 online, 有興趣可以入黎一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我開poat叫人去我個ser, 你就入黎叫人去第二度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d1216ce4ccb56e5a7eeb18c0eebd5262b3368e","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同Minecraft最大分別係咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅石系統變左，可以先己選點樣link, 變化大左， 雖然依家新game 未有人整d 好複雜既結構出黎<br />\n<br />\nteleport 可以定向， 我依家個屋企起左個好似主城咁既 teleport interchange<br />\n<br />\n有得Claim 地做地主，可以係自己領地較setting 防止自己屋企比人一個super TNT 炸爆左/一把火燒晒<br />\n<br />\n有得用藍圖， 有得跟佢砌或者直接起比你好似， 我未用過呢個<br />\n<br />\n仲有adventure gate 比你用人地整既副本/迷宮之類既野， 你都可以整一個黎比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多左怪既種類， d 怪會出技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢有免費版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n畫面靚d 音效好d<br />\n<br />\n然後minecraft 有既野佢都有， 除左未有咁多mod, 新既&quot;紅石&quot;system , 新既 engine 都有好大既潛力比作者發揮/比人整mod<br />\n<br />\n我會話Minecraft 既終點會係呢隻Game 既起點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea843a45ff349ddcee854f49ebf538f3a8963376","tid":245804,"uid":103717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我同班fd 入左個 public ser 叫「Asia Public Server」<br />\n<br />\n入面既玩家大多都好nice , server 長期有大約10個人 online, 有興趣可以入黎一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我開poat叫人去我個ser, 你就入黎叫人去第二度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry 當我無講過，請大家入樓主個ser"},{"pid":"f8b783be449e83107c09525c831c609f7337cb30","tid":245804,"uid":64378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我同班fd 入左個 public ser 叫「Asia Public Server」<br />\n<br />\n入面既玩家大多都好nice , server 長期有大約10個人 online, 有興趣可以入黎一齊玩</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n我開poat叫人去我個ser, 你就入黎叫人去第二度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry 當我無講過，請大家入樓主個ser</blockquote><br />\n其實無所謂既<img src=\"/assets/face